text:
Fuyuko
Could you take a look at this real quick?

It's the draft for an article about the recent live
......Here you go.

Surely you weren't expecting Fuyu to get excited
about something like this, right?

Did you think if you showed me this picture,
that you'd get to see Fuyu smile?

S-Sorry... Since you really stood out in this picture,
I thought you might be......

Well this is troubling. Fuyu's producer thinks that
she'd be delighted by something of this level...

Well, since you tried this hard to make Fuyu happy,
I guess I can play along.
